        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-03-11T20:24:47Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>End Taxpayer Subsidies for Drug Ads Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a tax deduction for expenses relating to direct-to-consumer advertising of prescription drugs. </p> <p><i>Direct-to-consumer advertising</i> is any dissemination, by or on behalf of a sponsor of a prescription drug product, of an advertisement that is in regard to the drug product and primarily targeted to the general public. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
